###########
## param ##
###########
# x64
RCX, RDX, R8, R9	=> 4 first arguments (other on the stack)



#############
## shorcut ##
#############
; /	 => ;=place a comment /=place comment in decompiler view
n	 => rename
g	 => jump to addr (in graph view)
Alt+M	 => bookmark
Ctrl+M	 => bookmark manager
Alt+B	 => Binary search
Ctrl+P	 => jump menu
> Ctrl+F => search in jump menu
x	 => (on a function) show ref of selected function
F5	 => Generate pseudocode (cloud decompiler service)



####################
## memory mapping ##
####################
# launch exe in windbg then: lm to find base address
# in IDA
Options > General > Line prefixes (graph)
Edit > Segments > Rebase program > update image base value
# symbols
File > Load file > PDB file


##############
## debugger ##
##############
F2		=> Add breakpoint
Ctrl+Alt+B	=> breakpoint list
F8		=> Step over

# on stack
Right clic > Data Format > Addr with text

# patch
Edit > Patch program > Assemble				# update assembly
Edit > Patch program > Apply patches to input file	# save update



